.\" termin.al-name: cat
.\" termin.al-usage: cat <path> [path ...]
.\" termin.al-summary: Print raw virtual document content.
.TH CAT 1 "" "termin.al" "termin.al Manual"
.ftr B R
.ftr I R
.ftr BI R
.SH NAME
cat \- Print raw virtual document content.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
cat <path> [path ...]
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
Writes one or more virtual documents to terminal scrollback without Markdown rendering. Documents are read in argument order.
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
$ cat about.md
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
help(1), man(1)
